# Plugins overlay directory.
#
# Plugins adapt Solaris for a domain/employer/repo-specific way of working. Each plugin is a folder
# here (e.g. plugins/nvidia-isaac-lab/). Plugins are user-private and gitignored; this committed
# placeholder just keeps the directory present on a fresh clone, and Solaris deletes it the first time
# a plugin is added.
#
# See solaris/spec/spec-v0.6.0.md (Plugins) and solaris/skills/import-plugin.skill.md.
